      </hedline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>When planning a trip into New York from my home in New Hampshire last winter, I discovered the CurtainUp site (www.curtainup .com). There is news of upcoming performances and reviews of current shows. The site has extensive coverage of the summer theater in the Berkshires, and the searchable archive of reviews gives me some insight on the productions playing at the local repertory companies.</p>
        <p>BILL BIER  Londonderry, N.H.</p>
      </block>
